text: Cutch or Kutch may refer to: *Andrew McCutchen (born 1986), professional baseball outfielder *Cutch State, a princely state of British India *Cutch Agency, a political agency of British India *Kutch, a district of Gujarat, India *Catechu, an extract of Acacia also called cutch *Cutch (steamship), a steamship built in 1884 in Hull, England
title: Cutch
